## Automated Workflows

1. Code Analysis:
   - Run on file changes
   - Check against style guides
   - Validate types
   - Scan for security issues
   - Monitor performance impact
   - Track technical debt

2. Documentation:
   - Auto-generate on changes
   - Update README files
   - Maintain CHANGELOG
   - Track API changes
   - Generate type docs
   - Update examples

3. Testing:
   - Run unit tests
   - Integration testing
   - Performance benchmarks
   - Security scanning
   - Coverage reporting
   - Automated fixes

## Process Management

1. Version Control:
   - Auto-branch naming
   - Commit message validation
   - PR templates
   - Branch protection
   - Merge requirements
   - Change tracking

2. Deployment:
   - Automated staging
   - Production safeguards
   - Rollback procedures
   - Health checks
   - Performance monitoring
   - Error tracking

3. Maintenance:
   - Dependency updates
   - Security patches
   - Cache clearing
   - Log rotation
   - Backup procedures
   - Health reporting 